{"tid":690531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小行星直衝地球，並已在非洲上空解體","createTime":"2018-06-05T03:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T08:44:03.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f8c68c9e0ad5f03657e037e85103b370cfc1b323","tid":690531,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T03:09:39.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180605/s00005/08b7c9d9d0a693fea9e29c96a0a5764b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180605%2Fs00005%2F08b7c9d9d0a693fea9e29c96a0a5764b.jpg&h=03e612c4&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n直徑約長2米的「2018 LA」小行星上周六凌晨被發現位於月球軌道附近，直衝地球<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，數小時後在非洲南部博茨瓦納上空解體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。網上流傳片段所見，南非北部接壤博茨瓦納地區一個農場的夜空有一點光飛近，光點愈變愈大並閃出強光<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一瞬間照亮整個夜空<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n小行星「2018 LA」是歷史上第三次被科學家發現直飛地球的小行星，而三次都是由天文學家考瓦爾斯基（Richard Kowalski）以設在美國亞利桑那州圖森市的卡特琳那巡天系统（Catalina Sky Survey）所發現。一顆直徑4米的小行星2008年在進入地球前19小時被發現，並如預測在非洲蘇丹上空解體，而第二次則在在2014年，一顆小行星進入地球前數小時才被發現，最終在大西洋上空解體。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180605/s00005/1528164170868\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180605%2Fs00005%2F1528164170868&d=AZAWpLf1Nx5nkV5bLvirGi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=cec0305c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180605%2Fs00005%2F1528164170868&h=7e93f203\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180605/s00005/1528164170868</a>"},{"pid":"a5870cb072171108253242ce7b40166fc183a70b","tid":690531,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T03:10:17.000Z","msg":"美國太空總署（NASA）在小行星墜落地球前8小時才發現它會直衝地球。<br />\n<br />\n美國太空總署承認，今次追蹤行動有點急，在發現「2018 LA」後很快就確定其體積，認為對地球威脅不大，有助將來預測飛向地球的巨型小行星做好準備。"},{"pid":"c6e945e14fbfc06d604e44564e39511606e37d69","tid":690531,"uid":166462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T03:11:47.000Z","msg":"4M <br />\n短撚過招牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a73d83c46cb23ad5a6890f64adfc3e95a6a7d6","tid":690531,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T03:13:00.000Z","msg":"Transformer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea22172f8455a9b4d89a07e8fd8606ec0c408cd2","tid":690531,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T03:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> wing zero custom一下射爆佢"},{"pid":"490a82837c224d3bfaf3ff0b01fd8466f43b0c2d","tid":690531,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T03:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/05/111440_043ab0ec0976b0963523d742dc22973c.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F05%2F111440_043ab0ec0976b0963523d742dc22973c.PNG&h=3cb79d39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4f1f825c49c1f12c6779f6138026a3f0463e477","tid":690531,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T03:15:13.000Z","msg":"vibranium"},{"pid":"4a93d080c81daf64c09ce2b92f06306a6cb37ee1","tid":690531,"uid":150935,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T03:15:32.000Z","msg":"Wakanda forever!"},{"pid":"64c37e056034e8c7e88a5603ccc49a678dd74c66","tid":690531,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T03:39:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3dae4874789470083f5199329c4c4a3affc69779","tid":690531